#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Max's observation: the extensions rising fastest are \"the boring ones\" — the tools you need to actually build and run a production service. The novelty extensions (AI, reactive, event-driven frameworks) appear further down the list and take time to climb."
msgstr "马克斯的观察：增长最快的扩展正是“那些看似枯燥的”——也就是实际构建和运行生产环境服务所必需的工具。而那些新潮的扩展（如AI、响应式、事件驱动框架等）则排在列表更靠后的位置，需要时间才能攀升。"

