#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Java remains dominant at nearly 97% of builds. Kotlin grew almost 12% year-over-year in absolute terms — still a small share, but meaningful enough that the team treats Kotlin investment as informed by real data rather than guesswork."
msgstr "Java 仍占据主导地位，占比近 97%。Kotlin 的绝对增长量同比增加了近 12%——虽然占比仍很小，但这一增长足以让团队基于真实数据而非猜测来决定对 Kotlin 的投入。"

