#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What This Data Drives"
msgstr "这些数据推动了什么"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Bruno and Max were both clear that the analytics are not vanity metrics. Kotlin adoption data informs how much the team invests in Kotlin support. Gradle's share informs tooling investment. Extension growth rates influence where limited engineering resources get focused. The Java version distribution directly shaped the decision to target Java 21+ for Quarkus 4."
msgstr "布鲁诺和马克斯都明确表示，这些分析数据并非虚荣指标。Kotlin 的采用数据决定了团队在 Kotlin 支持方面投入多少资源；Gradle 的市场份额决定了工具方面的投入；扩展功能的增长率则影响着有限的工程资源应重点投入何处；而 Java 版本的分布情况直接促成了将 Quarkus 4 定位为支持 Java 21 及以上版本的决策。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The team encouraged anyone not yet opted in — especially Kotlin or Gradle users — to enable the analytics, since the current numbers likely undercount those populations. More representative data leads to better prioritization decisions."
msgstr "该团队鼓励尚未选择加入的用户——尤其是 Kotlin 或 Gradle 用户——启用分析功能，因为当前的数据很可能低估了这些用户群体的规模。更具代表性的数据有助于做出更合理的优先级决策。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Upcoming"
msgstr "即将推出"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The episode also mentioned that Quarkus 3.37 has been released, and development on Quarkus 4 continues alongside the 3.x series (expected through 3.40). Quarkus Insights will be on a summer break for two weeks; the next episode will return to domain-driven design and hexagonal architecture."
msgstr "该期节目还提到，Quarkus 3.37 已正式发布，Quarkus 4 的开发工作正与 3.x 系列（预计将持续至 3.40 版本）同步进行。《Quarkus Insights》将休播两周以度过暑假；下一期节目将重返领域驱动设计和六边形架构的话题。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Key Takeaways"
msgstr "要点总结"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Build analytics are opt-in and anonymous** — only build metadata is collected, never source code or IP addresses."
msgstr "*构建分析功能采用主动参与模式且匿名* ——仅收集构建元数据，绝不会收集源代码或 IP 地址。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Monthly active users grew 16%** and total builds grew 26% year-over-year."
msgstr "*月活跃用户同比增长16* %，总构建量同比增长26%。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Windows 11 is now the most-used OS** among Quarkus developers, overtaking macOS."
msgstr "*Windows 11 现已成为* Quarkus 开发者中最 *常用的操作系统，* 超越了 macOS。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Java 25 adoption is at 22%** — faster than any previous Java version uptake; Java 21 + 25 together are 76% of all builds."
msgstr "*Java 25 的采用率达到 22%* ——这一增速超过了以往任何一个 Java 版本；Java 21 和 25 合计占所有构建的 76%。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Quarkus 4 will require Java 21+**, and the community is already largely ready."
msgstr "*Quarkus 4 将要求使用 Java 21 及以上版本* ，而社区方面基本上已经做好了准备。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Maven holds at 85%** of builds; Gradle at ~15%."
msgstr "*Maven 占* 构建总量的 *85%* ；Gradle 约占 15%。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Production-oriented \"boring\" extensions are growing fastest** — Flyway (+72%), JDBC (+42%), Vault, Quartz."
msgstr "*以生产为导向的“枯燥”扩展增长最快* ——Flyway（+72%）、JDBC（+42%）、Vault、Quartz。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**RESTEasy Classic migration is nearly complete** — the new REST Jackson extension is at 86% share."
msgstr "*RESTEasy Classic 的迁移工作已接近尾声* ——新的 REST Jackson 扩展的使用率已达到 86%。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**The community is diversifying geographically** — Latin America, India, and China are all growing strongly."
msgstr "*该社区在地理分布上日益多元化* ——拉丁美洲、印度和中国都呈现出强劲的增长势头。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**MCP server and Tika extensions are rising**, suggesting agentic workloads are moving from experimentation into real applications."
msgstr "*MCP 服务器和 Tika 扩展正日益普及* ，这表明代理型工作负载正从实验阶段转向实际应用。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Conclusion"
msgstr "结论"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The build analytics give the Quarkus team — and the wider community — a grounded, data-driven view of how Quarkus is being used in practice. The picture that emerges from May 2026 is of a maturing, production-focused ecosystem: developers are building more, upgrading Java versions faster than ever, reaching for production essentials like schema migration and secrets management, and coming from a more geographically diverse set of time zones than ever before."
msgstr "构建分析为 Quarkus 团队——以及更广泛的社区——提供了关于 Quarkus 在实际应用中如何被使用的、基于事实且数据驱动的视角。 2026年5月呈现出的图景是一个日趋成熟、以生产环境为中心的生态系统：开发者正在构建更多项目，Java版本的升级速度比以往任何时候都快，他们正积极采用模式迁移和密钥管理等生产环境必备功能，且其所在的时区分布比以往任何时候都更加广泛。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-06-30-quarkus-insights-253-build-analytics.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you want to help make the data more representative, you can enable build analytics by setting `disabled: false` in `~/.redhat/` — or just answer \"yes\" next time dev mode prompts you. Every build counts."
msgstr "如果您希望帮助提高数据的代表性，可以在 `~/.redhat/` 中将 `disabled: false` 设置为 true 来启用构建分析功能——或者在下次开发模式提示时直接回答“是”。每次构建都至关重要。"

