msgstr "请在 link:https://www.youtube.com/quarkusio[Quarkus YouTube 频道] 观看完整剧集。如需了解收集了哪些数据，请访问 link:https://quarkus.io/usage/[quarkus.io/usage] ；如需按人气排序浏览扩展程序，请访问 link:https://quarkus.io/extensions/[quarkus.io/extensions] 。"
